    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 with documented justification. Hemolysis index predictions satisfy the validation acceptance criterion (NIH within 2 experimental standard deviations at all five operating points, GCI 4.7%). The computational model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device within the operating envelope defined in the sponsor's predicate comparison strategy (1–6 L/min, 2000–4000 RPM). Assessment accepted for inclusion in pre-market submission package.",
